{"tid":2513914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"舉重昏迷｜健身男留院6日不治","createTime":"2021-05-03T02:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T02:27:35.000Z","uid":17387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d12b9b45026a1daaf7e10fa26fb42569b625ed70","tid":2513914,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"41歲姓王男子，上周二（4月27日）在上水天平商場一間24小時營業的健身中心內舉重期間昏迷。職員發現王的時候，其胸前壓住槓鈴。王留院6日，至昨天（5月2日）中午12時41分不治。涉事健身室暫未發聲明回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上周二清晨6時半，職員由CCTV發現事主舉起槓鈴後暈倒，倒卧在一部「史密夫機」附近，連忙報警。據了解，男子暈倒至職員發現之間，相差3分鐘。而槓鈴的槓鈴桿重20公斤，加上兩端的鐵餅，估計最少也有30公斤。事件敲響24小時健身中心的安全警號，大學教授建議市民通宵時段宜結伴同行，以便有照應。有顧客認為24小時健身中心應安排職員當值，以策安全。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210503/F2JEKCZ7GRFEBD2IF4PWDP75AQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR15rHhd9BlZcZlJRLuf3s_NQiCCAe2xPsW3bjRClONfC-ttiAtbRu5y-is\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210503%2FF2JEKCZ7GRFEBD2IF4PWDP75AQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR15rHhd9BlZcZlJRLuf3s_NQiCCAe2xPsW3bjRClONfC-ttiAtbRu5y-is&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4699b9dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210503%2FF2JEKCZ7GRFEBD2IF4PWDP75AQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR15rHhd9BlZcZlJRLuf3s_NQiCCAe2xPsW3bjRClONfC-ttiAtbRu5y-is&h=0fa9ea14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210503/F2JEKCZ7GRFEBD2IF4PWDP75AQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR15rHhd9BlZcZlJRLuf3s_NQiCCAe2xPsW3bjRClONfC-ttiAtbRu5y-is</a>"},{"pid":"157b49d61d0994ed60cb61658b2c1d3878188c76","tid":2513914,"